            <div class="post-content-inner">
              
              We use this: <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.topdesk.nl/">http://www.topdesk.nl/</a><!-- m --><br /><br />It's fast, runs in the browser and you can configure it as you like.<br /><br />It's based on the ITIL mindset though, don't know if that is a good fit for your company.<br /><br />The biggest advantage is that it is fast to create tickets and resolve them.

              

              
              
            </div>
          </td>
