        <tr>
          <td class="post-content">
            <div class="post-content-inner">
              
              I have worked with many a ticketing system.  With 100 users and 2 responders, they are all overkill and will slow you down.  You should just use a shared mailbox or something.<br /><br />Here's what I use now: <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://inboxharmony.com/">http://inboxharmony.com/</a><!-- m --><br /><br />My other favorite one, with 5-10 responders, would be <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://roundup.sourceforge.net/">http://roundup.sourceforge.net/</a><!-- m -->  But it requires configuration.<br /><br />For 10+ responders and many projects, maybe RT?

              

              
              
            </div>
          </td>
        </tr>
        
    </table>
    
