              Our IT support desks use RT (Request Tracker) from <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.bestpractical.com/rt/">http://www.bestpractical.com/rt/</a><!-- m --><br /><br />It's fairly easy to setup, has lots of extensibility if you're into perl and our helpdesk users seem very happy with it.

              

              
              
