              We have been using spiceworks here where I work. We are about 250 users with 4 responders.<br /><br />It's a free ticketing app that seems to work pretty well. So far does everything we need it to do.<br /><br />They also have an active user community that can help answer questions. <br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.spiceworks.com/">http://www.spiceworks.com/</a><!-- m -->

              

              
              
